'''哥打白沙罗站'''（{{lang-ms|Stesen MRT Kota Damansara}}）位於[[雪兰莪|雪兰莪]][[哥打白沙罗|哥打白沙罗]]丽阳医院对面，是[[巴生谷捷运|巴生谷]][[双溪毛糯－加影线|双溪毛糯－加影线]]的其中一个[[高架车站|高架]][[捷运|捷运]]车站。本站属于双加捷运第一阶段线路，于2016年12月16日开始运营。<ref name=MRT>{{cite news|title=首相正式启动第一阶段双加线|url=http://www.mymrt.com.my/cms/upload_files/mediarelease/mediarelease_download_000923.pdf|accessdate=19 December 2016|publisher=Mass Rapid Transit Corporation Sdn Bhd|date=15 December 2016|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170305001836/http://www.mymrt.com.my/cms/upload_files/mediarelease/mediarelease_download_000923.pdf|archivedate=2017年3月5日}}</ref><ref name=Malay16122016>{{cite news|last1=Ruban|first1=A.|title=A quiet start to Malaysia’s first MRT, but commuters happy|url=http://www.themalaymailonline.com/malaysia/article/a-quiet-start-to-malaysias-first-mrt-but-commuters-happy|accessdate=2016-12-18|work=The Malay Mail Online|date=2016-12-16|archive-date=2017-08-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170804101820/http://www.themalaymailonline.com/malaysia/article/a-quiet-start-to-malaysias-first-mrt-but-commuters-happy|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=捷运双加线首阶段通车．双溪毛糯至士曼丹免费乘搭1个月|url=http://www.sinchew.com.my/node/1596685/捷运双加线首阶段通车．双溪毛糯至士曼丹免费乘搭1个月|accessdate=2017-07-22|publisher=[[星洲网|星洲网]]|date=2017-12-16|language=zh-hans|archive-date=2019-05-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190511101145/http://www.sinchew.com.my/node/1596685/%E6%8D%B7%E8%BF%90%E5%8F%8C%E5%8A%A0%E7%BA%BF%E9%A6%96%E9%98%B6%E6%AE%B5%E9%80%9A%E8%BD%A6%EF%BC%8E%E5%8F%8C%E6%BA%AA%E6%AF%9B%E7%B3%AF%E8%87%B3%E5%A3%AB%E6%9B%BC%E4%B8%B9%E5%85%8D%E8%B4%B9%E4%B9%98%E6%90%AD1%E4%B8%AA%E6%9C%88|dead-url=no}}</ref>

