==接驳巴士==
加影线车站皆提供接驳巴士服务。本站提供前往[[哥打白沙罗|哥打白沙罗]]若干工业和住宅区的服务，将停留位于街道旁巴士站。<ref>{{cite news|title=捷运接驳巴士路线|url=http://www.spad.gov.my/land-public-transport/buses/mrt-feeder-bus-routes|accessdate=2017-07-20|publisher=[[陆路公共交通委员会|陆路公共交通委员会]]|language=en|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170723130349/http://www.spad.gov.my/land-public-transport/buses/mrt-feeder-bus-routes|archive-date=2017-07-23|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=MRT Kota Damansara (T805) & (T806) - Door A|url=http://www.spad.gov.my/sites/default/files/mrt_kota_damansara_t805_t806_pintu_a.pdf|publisher=[[陆路公共交通委员会|陆路公共交通委员会]]|language=en|access-date=2017-07-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170807221156/http://www.spad.gov.my/sites/default/files/mrt_kota_damansara_t805_t806_pintu_a.pdf|archive-date=2017-08-07|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=MRT Kota Damansara (T805) & (T806) - Door B|url=http://www.spad.gov.my/sites/default/files/mrt_kota_damansara_t805_t806_pintu_b.pdf|accessdate=2017-07-20|publisher=[[陆路公共交通委员会|陆路公共交通委员会]]|language=en|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170821231235/http://www.spad.gov.my/sites/default/files/mrt_kota_damansara_t805_t806_pintu_b.pdf|archive-date=2017-08-21|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

